caption.p: SEM images of TiO 2 NTs obtained from the anodization of Ti-6Al-4V alloy in fluoride ethylene glycol electrolyte with different water contents: 20 wt% H 2O (top view in the inset) ( a) and 25 wt% H 2O ( b), and the energy-dispersive spectroscopy (EDS) elemental spectrum of the anodized Ti-6Al-4V alloy ( c).
